title: Democratic senators press Commerce Secretary Lutnick on conflict of interest concerns in USA Rare Earth deal
summary_full: Sens. Elizabeth Warren, Chris Van Hollen and Ron Wyden are pressing Commerce Secretary Howard Lutnick for more information on the USA Rare Earth deal.
